StoneRidge Investment Partners offers equity investment management to institutional investors. StoneRidge was formed in 1999 and restructured in 2009, when Steven Sanders was named CEO & Chief Investment Strategist. Mr. Sanders and founding principals, Philip Brown, President and Joseph Stocke, Chief Investment Officer, continue to guide and lead our organization in providing world-class asset management services to our clients.
